OL,3,COil and gas workers unwilling to board
OL,4,CSuper Pumas over safety fears, poll
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHundreds of North Sea oil and gas
OL,8,Fworkers have vowed to never again set
OL,9,Ffoot on a model of helicopter involved
OL,10,Fin a series of fatal crashes amid
OL,11,Fspeculation about their potential
OL,12,Freintroduction.
OL,14,FA survey of 1,200 staff carried out by
OL,15,Fthe union Unite found three-quarters
OL,16,Fof workers are unwilling to board
OL,17,FSuper Pumas.
OL,19,FSuper Pumas were removed from the oil
OL,20,Fand gas sector in 2016 in the wake of
OL,21,Fthe accidents.
