OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe Unite poll was carried out after a
OL,8,Fnumber of safety concerns were
OL,9,Frecently raised about helicopters
OL,10,Fflying workers to and from offshore
OL,11,Finstallations and platforms.
OL,13,FOne person was killed and five others
OL,14,Fwere injured when a Sikorsky S-92,
OL,15,Foperated by Bristow for the Norwegian
OL,16,Ffirm Equinor, ditched into the sea
OL,17,Fnear Bergen in February.
