OL,3,COil and gas workers unwilling to board
OL,4,CSuper Pumas over safety fears, poll
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe S-92 is the primary helicopter
OL,8,Fused across the UK and Norway, but a
OL,9,Frecent shortage of spare parts has
OL,10,Fseen some of the aircraft grounded.
OL,12,FPolled on the possible reintroduction
OL,13,Fof flights on Super Pumas, 75% of
OL,14,Fstaff said they would never fly in one
OL,15,Fagain, with 18% saying they would need
OL,16,Fto be convinced all outstanding safety
OL,17,Fconcerns had been fully addressed.
