OL,4,CSuper Pumas over safety fears, poll
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FQuestioned about the Sikorsky S-92
OL,8,Fhelicopters, 43% expressed concerns
OL,9,Fover supply chains impacting safety,
OL,10,F36% said they had confidence in the
OL,11,Faircraft, and 17% said they had been
OL,12,F"really shaken" by the February crash.
OL,14,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,15,Fsaid: "Unite will never, ever allow
OL,16,Foffshore health and safety to be
OL,17,Fcompromised by operators and
OL,18,Fcontractors.
