OL,3,COil and gas workers unwilling to board
OL,4,CSuper Pumas over safety fears, poll
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Absolutely central to this objective
OL,8,Fis ensuring the full confidence of
OL,9,Foffshore workers in the helicopters
OL,10,Fwhich they are transported in.
OL,12,F"Overwhelmingly, offshore workers are
OL,13,Ftelling Unite that more action and
OL,14,Fassurances are needed from the
OL,15,Findustry in order to improve the
OL,16,Fsafety of helicopter flights.
OL,18,F"Operators and contractors must listen
OL,19,Fto these concerns and act."
