OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FJohn Boland, Unite's lead officer in
OL,8,Fthe offshore sector, added: "Unite
OL,9,Fwill ensure that concerns over
OL,10,Fhelicopter safety are fully addressed
OL,11,Fby the oil and gas industry.
OL,13,F"Offshore workers have clearly spoken
OL,14,Fabout their horror over the Super Puma
OL,15,Fmodel ever being reintroduced and have
OL,16,Falso expressed their concerns about
OL,17,Fsupply chain issues impacting on the
OL,18,Fsafety of the Sikorsky S-92 helicopter.
