OL,7,F"The industry must take note of what
OL,8,Foffshore workers are saying and work
OL,9,Fwith Unite to resolve these safety
OL,10,Fconcerns."
OL,12,FFourteen oil workers and two crew died
OL,13,Fwhen a Bond Super Puma plunged into
OL,14,Fwater off the Aberdeenshire coast on
OL,15,FApril 1, 2009.
OL,17,FAn Air Accidents Investigation Branch
OL,18,Fprobe into the crash found the
OL,19,Faircraft suffered a "catastrophic
OL,20,Ffailure" of its main rotor gearbox.
