OL,8,Falso found the tragedy could have been
OL,9,Favoided.
OL,11,FFour years later, four people died
OL,12,Fwhen a Super Puma L2 carrying oil rig
OL,13,Fworkers ditched in the North Sea near
OL,14,FSumburgh, Shetland, in August 2013.
OL,16,FAn FAI found no precautions could have
OL,17,Fprevented the crash after a "perfect
OL,18,Fstorm" of circumstances combined.
